xgo.set_servo_angle|block: Set the servo rotation value of the %joint joint of the %part leg to %angle degrees
xgo.single_leg|block: Set the X position of the tip of the %part leg to %location_x,Y position to %location_y,Z position to %location_z
xgo.translational_step|block: Set XGO to perform a %direction translational motion with a step size of %step mm
xgo.translational_step_continue|block: Set XGO to perform a %direction translational motion with a step size of %step mm for %time seconds
xgo.rotate_angle|block: Set XGO to perform a %direction rotation at a speed of %speed degrees per second
xgo.rotate_angle_continue|block: Set XGO to perform a %direction rotation at a speed of %speed degrees per second for %time seconds
xgo.leg_lift|block: Set XGO execution to run in place at a fixed frequency at a leg lift height of %mm mm
xgo.leg_lift_continue|block: Set XGO execution to run in place at a fixed frequency at a leg lift height of %mm mm for %time seconds
xgo.translational_motion|block: et the XGO's body to pan %distance mm in the %direction_xyz direction
xgo.translational_motion_reciprocate|blo: Set XGO to move back and forth in the %direction_xyz direction with a period of %period second
xgo.translational_motion_reciprocate_sto: Stop the periodic translation of XGO in the  %direction_xyz direction
xgo.rotate_angle_reel|block: Set XGO to be rotated %angle degrees about the %direction_xyz axis
xgo.rotate_angle_reel_reciprocate|block: Set XGO to rotate around the %direction_xyz axis with a period of %period seconds
xgo.rotate_angle_reel_reciprocate_stop|b: Stop the periodic rotation of XGO around the %direction_xyz axis
xgo.servo_setting|block: %on_off the servo for the XGO's %part leg
xgo.get_servo_angle|block: Get the servo Angle of the %joint %part leg joint
